    "description": "We had so much fun playing with all these toys, but we can't just leave all of this mess behind!<br>Don't worry though, the excitement is not over yet, we're about to learn how organizing your mess can be a whole new way of having fun.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Practice your organization skills and critical thinking:</li></ul>Simple to understand, just drag and drop all the pieces and try to fit everything inside the boxes.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 99 levels and 54 different types of toys to organize:</li></ul>Many shapes and designs appear throughout the levels to keep the gameplay fresh.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Super secret ending for the completionists:</li></ul>Did you beat all the levels? Surprise! There's even more! New levels with extra challenge and a second ending are waiting for you.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cute and colorful graphics:</li></ul>Friendly for a younger audience, fun and challenging for the entire family.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Easy to play:</li></ul>Just use your computer mouse! Click, drag and drop the pieces. That's all you gotta do to master the game!<br>Stuck in a level? You can skip a few puzzles and come back to them later when you have more practice.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Original music:</li></ul>Fun soundtrack with toy-like sounds specially made for the game.",
